hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 混合物的质量守恒：
   $$A_1j_1 = A_2j_2\;\Longrightarrow\;j_2 = \sigma j_1,\quad\sigma \equiv \frac{A_1}{A_2}.$$
2. 气相的质量守恒：
   $$A_1j_{g1} = A_2j_{g2}\;\Longrightarrow\;j_{g2} = \sigma j_{g1}.$$
3. 截面 1 和 2 处的漂移通量关系：
   $$j_{g1} = \alpha_1\bigl(C_0j_1+v_{gj}\bigr),\qquad 
     j_{g2} = \alpha_2\bigl(C_0j_2+v_{gj}\bigr).$$
4. 将气体连续性方程与漂移通量关系式结合：
   $$\alpha_2\bigl(C_0j_2+v_{gj}\bigr)
     = \sigma\alpha_1\bigl(C_0j_1+v_{gj}\bigr)
     \;\Longrightarrow\;
     \frac{\alpha_2}{\alpha_1}
     = \sigma\;\frac{C_0j_1+v_{gj}}{C_0j_2+v_{gj}}
     = \sigma\;\frac{C_0j_1+v_{gj}}{C_0\sigma j_1+v_{gj}}.$$
5. 应用临界流动条件
   $$j_1 = \frac{v_{gj}}{C_0-1}.$$
   则
   $$
   C_0j_1+v_{gj}
   = \frac{C_0v_{gj}}{C_0-1}+v_{gj}
   = \frac{(2C_0-1)}{C_0-1}v_{gj},$$
   $$
   C_0\sigma j_1+v_{gj}
   = \frac{C_0\sigma v_{gj}}{C_0-1}+v_{gj}
   = \frac{C_0(\sigma+1)-1}{C_0-1}v_{gj}.$$
6. 代入并化简（消去公因式 $(C_0-1)$ 和 $v_{gj}$）：
   $$
   \frac{\alpha_2}{\alpha_1}
   = \sigma\;\frac{\displaystyle\frac{(2C_0-1)}{C_0-1}v_{gj}}
                   {\displaystyle\frac{C_0(\sigma+1)-1}{C_0-1}v_{gj}}
   = \frac{\sigma(2C_0-1)}{C_0(\sigma+1)-1}.
   $$
